      *****************************************************************
     C           INIT      BEGSR                           ***  INIT  ***
      *
      ** Set up copyright parameter
     C                     MOVEACPY@      CPY2@  80
      *
      ***  Receive Parameter List.
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PSEQ    5
     C                     PARM           PLEV    1
     C                     PARM           PENT    3
     C                     PARM           PPARM 100
      *
      ***  Initialise LDA field.
     C                     MOVEL'DL0728'  DBPGM
      *
      ***  Call Access Program for Bank Details - Title, Run Date and
      ***  Run Day Number.
     C                     CALL 'AOBANKR0'
     C                     PARM '*MSG   ' WRTCD   7
     C                     PARM '*FIRST ' WOPTN   7
     C           SDBANK    PARM SDBANK    DSFDY
      *
      ***  Handle Database Error.
      *
     C           WRTCD     IFNE *BLANKS
     C           *LOCK     IN   LDA
     C                     MOVE 'SDBANKPD'DBFILE           ***************
     C                     Z-ADD001       DBASE            * DB ERROR 01 *
     C                     OUT  LDA                        ***************
     C                     EXSR *PSSR
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      ***  Check System Date Format, DDMMYY (*IN98 off)
      ***                            MMDDYY (*IN98 on).
      *
     C           BJDFIN    IFEQ 'M'
     C                     SETON                     98
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      *
     C           *NAMVAR   DEFN           RUNDAT
     C           *NAMVAR   DEFN           LDA
     C                     IN   RUNDAT
      *
      ***  RCF Processing for File.
     C                     EXSR RCFP1
     C                     EXSR RCFAU
      *
      ***  Report Work fields.
      *
     C                     Z-ADD0         RQDLN1  30
     C                     Z-ADD0         DIFLN1  30
      *
     C                     ENDSR
