      /TITLE SR/PROCES
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  PROCES - Subroutine to do the Detail Processing.             *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By: Main Processing                                   *
      *  Calls:                                                       *
      *  REPORT - Process Report Lines                                *
      *  WP1END - Write End of Report                                 *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
     C           PROCES    BEGSR                           *** PROCES ***
      *
     C                     MOVE *OFF      *IN70
     C                     MOVE *OFF      *IN71
      * Process according to whether previous, future or all rollovers
      * are requested
      *
B1   C           TYPE      IFEQ 'P'
     C           TYPE      OREQ 'A'
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *IN70
      * Access deals file and print details, then if rollover of
      * deal number not blank, access deals file and get details
      * of this deal. Continue until no more.
     C           DLNUM     CHAINDEALSALL             80
B2   C           *IN80     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE 'DEALSALL'DBFILE
     C                     MOVE DLNUM     DBKEY
     C                     MOVE '001'     DBASE
     C                     EXSR *PSSR
X2   C                     ELSE
     C                     WRITEHEAD
     C                     EXSR REPORT
      *
     C           RODN      DOWNE0
     C           RODN      CHAINDEALSALL             80
B3   C           *IN80     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE 'DEALSALL'DBFILE
     C                     MOVE RODN      DBKEY
     C                     MOVE '002'     DBASE
     C                     EXSR *PSSR
E3   C                     ENDIF
     C                     EXSR REPORT
     C           RODN      CHAINDEALSALL             80
      *
     C                     ENDDO
      *
E2   C                     ENDIF
E1   C                     ENDIF
      *
B1   C           TYPE      IFEQ 'F'
     C           TYPE      OREQ 'A'
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *IN71
      * Access deals file and print details, then if rolled over by
      * deal number not blank, access deals file and get details
      * of this deal. Continue until no more.
     C           DLNUM     CHAINDEALSALL             80
B2   C           *IN80     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE 'DEALSALL'DBFILE
     C                     MOVE DLNUM     DBKEY
     C                     MOVE '003'     DBASE
     C                     EXSR *PSSR
X2   C                     ELSE
     C                     WRITEHEAD
     C                     EXSR REPORT
      *
     C           RBDN      DOWNE0
     C           RBDN      CHAINDEALSALL             80
B3   C           *IN80     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE 'DEALSALL'DBFILE
     C                     MOVE RBDN      DBKEY
     C                     MOVE '004'     DBASE
     C                     EXSR *PSSR
E3   C                     ENDIF
     C                     EXSR REPORT
     C           RBDN      CHAINDEALSALL             80
      *
     C                     ENDDO
      *
E2   C                     ENDIF
E1   C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     EXSR WP1END
      *
     C                     ENDSR
