      *****************************************************************
      /TITLE SR/REPORT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  REPORT - Process Report Lines.                               *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By: PROCES                                            *
      *  Calls:                                                       *
      *  WP1REC - Format and Write a Detail Record to the Report      *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
     C           REPORT    BEGSR                           *** REPORT ***
      *
      * Move Details to report fields
     C                     MOVE DLNO      PDLNO
     C                     MOVE CNUM      PCNUM
      *
      *  Get customer shortname
     C                     MOVELCNUM      @KEY1
     C                     CALL 'AOCUSTR0'
     C                     PARM *BLANKS   @RTCD   7
     C                     PARM '*KEY   ' @OPTN   7
     C                     PARM           @KEY1  10
     C                     PARM *BLANKS   @KYST   7
     C           SDCUST    PARM SDCUST    DSSDY
     C           @RTCD     IFEQ *BLANKS
     C                     MOVE BBCSSN    PSNAM
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   PSNAM
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           *IN70     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE RODN      PRODN
     C                     ENDIF
     C           *IN71     IFEQ *ON
     C                     MOVE RBDN      PRBDN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE FSSOFD    PSRFD
     C                     MOVE CCY       PCCY
      *
     C                     Z-ADDPCPL      ZFLD
     C                     CALL 'ZSEDIT'
     C                     PARM           ZFLD   150
     C                     PARM           ZDECS   10
     C                     PARM 'J'       ZECODE  1
     C                     PARM           ZOUT21 21
     C                     MOVE ZOUT21    PPCPL
      *
     C                     CALL 'ZDATE2'
     C                     PARM           VDAT
     C                     PARM           BJDFIN
     C                     PARM           ZDATE   60
     C                     PARM           ZADATE  7
     C                     MOVE ZDATE     PVDAT
      *
     C                     CALL 'ZDATE2'
     C                     PARM           MDAT
     C                     PARM           BJDFIN
     C                     PARM           ZDATE   60
     C                     PARM           ZADATE  7
     C                     MOVE ZDATE     PMDAT
      *
      * Edit interest rate
     C                     MOVE INTR      ZFIELD
     C                     Z-ADD7         ZDECS
     C                     CALL 'ZEDIT'
     C                     PARM           ZFIELD 16
     C                     PARM           ZDECS   10
     C                     MOVELZFIELD    PINTR
      *
     C                     MOVE ICBS      PICBS
      *
      * Edit interest paid to date
     C                     Z-ADDIPRD      ZFLD15
     C                     Z-ADD0         ZDECS
     C                     CALL 'ZSEDIT'
     C                     PARM           ZFLD15 150
     C                     PARM           ZDECS   10
     C                     PARM 'J'       ZECODE  1
     C                     PARM           ZOUT21 21
     C                     MOVELZOUT21    PIPRD
      *
     C                     MOVE FSBLKA    PBLKI
      *
     C                     Z-ADD4         RQDLN1
     C           OFLLN1    SUB  PRTLN1    DIFLN1
     C           DIFLN1    IFLE RQDLN1
     C                     WRITEHEAD
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     WRITEDETAIL
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *
      *****************************************************************
      /TITLE SR/WP1END
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  WP1END - Subroutine to Write End of Report.                  *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By: PROCES                                            *
      *  Calls    : None                                              *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           WP1END    BEGSR                           *** WP1END ***
      *
      ***  Check that sufficient lines remain for the Format. If not,
      ***  write out the Main Headings on a new page.
      *
     C                     Z-ADD4         RQDLN1
     C           OFLLN1    SUB  PRTLN1    DIFLN1
     C           DIFLN1    IFLE RQDLN1
     C                     WRITEHEAD
     C                     ENDIF
